An application named webapp has two versions in namespace production, an v1 and v2.
Both versions must be accessible over Service named webapp-svc.

Approximately 80% of traffic should be routed to v1.
Approximately 20% of traffic should be routed to v2.

Use only Kubernetes native objects.
Do not use Ingress, Service Mesh, or external load balancers.

Configure the required Kubernetes resources to satisfy the above requirements.
